    {
      "id": "SJbVaox5q8QK0wQ1rMqo-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 198.25,
      "y": 1135.3333740234375,
      "width": 441.05712890625,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 675048337,
      "version": 173,
      "versionNonce": 133650687,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775134915133,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.  Significant shift in side channel attack from same-core\nto cross-core execution.\n\n2.  Priors attacks focus on L1 cache, which is private to a core\nand not shared.\n\n3. Flush + Reload targets L3 cache, which contains copies\nof data stored in lower caches. This allows the spy and the\nvictim to execute in parallel on different cores.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.  Significant shift in side channel attack from same-core\nto cross-core execution.\n\n2.  Priors attacks focus on L1 cache, which is private to a core\nand not shared.\n\n3. Flush + Reload targets L3 cache, which contains copies\nof data stored in lower caches. This allows the spy and the\nvictim to execute in parallel on different cores.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
