      "seed": 944507601,
      "version": 274,
      "versionNonce": 368655985,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775134726011,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.  uses page sharing to reduce the memory footprint of \nmulti-tenanted systems by ensuring that \nidentical memory pages are not replicated.\n\n2.  Content-Aware Sharing: Identifies identical pages\nbased on their source.\n\n3. Content-Based Sharing (De-duplication): the system \nscans active memory to coalesce unrelated pages\nwith identical contents into a single physical page.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.  uses page sharing to reduce the memory footprint of \nmulti-tenanted systems by ensuring that \nidentical memory pages are not replicated.\n\n2.  Content-Aware Sharing: Identifies identical pages\nbased on their source.\n\n3. Content-Based Sharing (De-duplication): the system \nscans active memory to coalesce unrelated pages\nwith identical contents into a single physical page.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
