      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The square-and-multiply-always\nalgorithm is to create a uniform\nexecution trace regardless of the\nsecret data being processed.",
